casebody.data:
No. 394,

Mise.

Bandy v. United States Attorney General. Petitioner pro se. Solicitor General Marshall, Assistant Attorney General Rogovin, Meyer Rothwacks and Richard B. Buhrman for respondent.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari denied.
